											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Wyll and the player bow to each other, and then slowly begin to dance. This one is sadder than before. The camer pans upwards as the dance continues, and the scene fades away.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;JLatino: Reuse dance anims, slow them down, fade to black as dance starts" />
